Garlock: Known for manufacturing high-performance sealing materials for harsh environments.
UTEC: Focuses on providing innovative sealing products, including PTFE V packing.
Kelcoind: A key player offering PTFE-based solutions for various industrial applications.
These companies focus on expanding their product portfolios, enhancing performance capabilities, and ensuring compliance with international standards to remain competitive in the market.

